Class RDFTranslator

java.lang.Object
  org.vivoweb.ingest.translate.RDFTranslator

public class RDFTranslator
extends Object

RDF Tranlator This class translates RDF from its current schema into the VIVO ontology. It uses RDFworkflows to manipulate the data

Author:
Stephen V. Williams swilliams@ctrip.ufl.edu
